user.biography:
Where Focus Goes, Energy Flows @RubaAliFit  
Gymshark & Womensbest Athlete

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by RUBA ALI  ربا علي in Almaza Bay with @gymshark, and @rubaalifit. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text:
What feels like the end, can be a new beginning. You choose. 🕊

@gymshark

CRUSH IT WORKOUT 😳🔥 Save it for later! 

Real results happen when you stop focusing on others and start focusing on the small & consistent steps you need to take to become better. Always show up for yourself with your best effort🙌🏼 

CIRCUIT ➡️ 30 secs each exercise | 4 rounds | 30-60 secs rest after each round - Sippin on @womensbest 

Tag your friends to try this with & go crush it! ⤵️

node.text: The most beautiful moments come unexpected 🤎

NEXEL LEVEL LEGS😳🔥 Save it for later! 

The best way to overcome a “plateau” is by switching up your routine to keep your body guessing what’s next. The human body adapts to stress, this means as you get stronger your training also needs to increase in difficulty. Keep it fun & challenging 👊🏽

METHOD ➡️ 12-15 reps per side | 4 sets | 30 secs rest 

Wearing @gymshark new vital seamless launching 8/12 @ 2 pm ET 

Tag your friends & go crush it! ⤵️

CRUSH IT WORKOUT🥵 Save it for later! 

Let your actions match your intentions.If you truly want something, PUT IN the WORK daily  to achieve it. Get serious about your goals, believe in yourself and make it happen!!💫 

METHOD➡️ 12-15 reps per side|4 sets |30 secs rest after each set

Tag your friends to try this with & go crush it! ⤵️ @gymshark
